 1<b>. Transfer to serving dish with quinoa and wild rice mixture. Add roasted carrots, reserved chopped herbs, zest and juice of limes and mix with spatula. Serve warm or cold."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve this rice with meat or poultry."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","45m","6 portions"]}